headline: DuPont Innovators in Semiconductor Materials Named 2025 Heroes of Chemistry
summary: DuPont (NYSE: DD) today announced that 13 of its current and former scientists and engineers have been named 2025 Heroes of Chemistry by the American Chemical Society (ACS) for an innovative program that progressed semiconductor lithography.
